g.text: Flow of enrolled international students from origin countries to major destination countries
Sources: USA IIE Open Doors (2023/24); UK HESA (2022/23); Australia Dept. of Education (2023);
Canada CBIE/IRCC (2023); Japan JASSO (2024); EU DAAD/Campus France estimates.
Student numbers represent total enrolled (stock) for the most recent available year.
